{"tid":2265299,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"前世妄想顛倒，諸煩惱生","createTime":"2020-10-31T10:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T10:52:36.000Z","uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cefe4d9aed1e1c0ad73e107ff2eabcb3cb278ca6","tid":2265299,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"何謂病本，謂有攀緣。從有攀緣則為病本。何所攀緣，謂之三界。云何斷攀緣，以無所得。若無所得，則無攀緣。何謂無所得，謂離二見。何謂二見，謂內見外見是無所得。文殊師利，是為有疾菩薩調伏其心，為斷老病死苦是菩薩菩提。"},{"pid":"24560bf52db72ea6f18fdb1f0ff6b88abca3f20b","tid":2265299,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:52:36.000Z","msg":"打J升仙煩惱散<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}